{"tid":1740911,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"(正視聽）區議會選舉唔需要配票 唔需要你口講投建制","createTime":"2019-11-20T06:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T07:12:07.000Z","uid":163149,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d19e014621380a2a4e42d93564cf85705790ca","tid":1740911,"uid":163149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:11:59.000Z","msg":"區議會選舉唔係立法會選舉呀...<br />\n一人一區一票， 建制唔會自己打到自己<br />\n如果唔係自己去撞區，其實冇配票策略可言<br />\n<br />\n區選可唔可以如期進行我唔太在意<br />\n因為香港既廢中廢老仍然拎住大量票<br />\n有好多你俾小恩小惠就換到既票數， 所以我唔會對區選有太大期望<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hSrRZqg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhSrRZqg.png&h=5884655d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係如果區選真係進行既， 我地就要行出黎投自己一票<br />\n而且今次唔會立法會選舉， <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔駛四圍同人講口投建制呀</span></span><br />\n冇配票策略駛鬼幫建制做勢？<br />\n見到呢個post 真係嘔嘔地血<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">收到SMS叫我星期日投票......<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1740694\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1740694</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n我地應該做既係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一票不投建制</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外俾多個網站大家睇候選人資料：<br />\n<a href=\"https://vote4.hk/zh/district/2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvote4.hk%2Fzh%2Fdistrict%2F2019&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=efb8f99f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vote4.hk/zh/district/2019</a>"},{"pid":"1ed9ca32cb1cc1fccdaf9fcae63351d980a866f1","tid":1740911,"uid":163149,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:18:48.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪再個個係度話投建制<br />\n連個勢都輸撚埋"},{"pid":"5182dd05dfdc34db75efe1b2adaacc86d7d92539","tid":1740911,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-